        "is_accepted": true,
        "last_activity_date": 1611063069,
        "creation_date": 1611062337,
        "body": "<p>there is a <code>sample(Duration)<\/code>, so you could do:<\/p>\n<pre><code>source.sample(Duration.ofMillis(100));\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>(100 milliseconds = 1/10th of a second, so you'd get at most 1 element every 100ms, ie. 10 elements every second)<\/p>\n<p>edit: for a proper <code>throttle<\/code>, consider also <code>sampleFirst(v -&gt; Mono.delay(Duration.ofMillis(100))<\/code> to drop all items that follow a propagated item within 100ms<\/p>\n",
